		data-flex-basis=&#34;180px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The event was jointly organized by the Foshan Law Society and the Foshan Lawyers Association, with sponsorship and support from JD Group&amp;rsquo;s Judicial Auction Platform.&lt;/p&gt;
